らなかった、新しい考え方を教えてもらえるから","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event115-04-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"つぐみ","body":"それが楽しくて、もっとがんばれるんじゃないかな","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event115-04-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":1}],"windowDisplayName":"香澄","body":"お〜！　これがツグってるってやつ？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":1,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":1,"voiceId":"event115-04-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"つぐみ","body":"あはは……そうかも。今だって、ここで学んだことを\nAfterglowでも早く試したくて、ウズウズしてるもん","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event115-04-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"つぐみ","body":"そしたらきっと、私達の演奏ももっとよくできるし……\nライブだって、もっといいものになる！","tention